{"article_id":"QkrzbM8iVWpk99Xm","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump has signed a $ 1.3 trillion spending plan","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to fund the government through September .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Lawmakers passed the bill in the wee hours of the morning Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and Trump had initially indicated","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"he might veto it ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"criticizing the lack of action on the DACA debate and his border wall .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"I am considering a VETO of the Omnibus Spending Bill","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"based on the fact","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"that the 800,000 plus DACA recipients have been totally abandoned by the Democrats","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"( not even mentioned in Bill )","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and the BORDER WALL ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"which is desperately needed for our National Defense ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"is not fully funded .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"March 23 , 2018","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Trump says","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"he only signed off on the bill on `` national security '' grounds","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"because it rebuilds America 's military","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"and improves homeland security .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"`` There are a lot of things","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"I 'm not happy about in this bill , ''","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Trump said Friday afternoon .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"`` I say to Congress","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"I will never sign a bill like this again . ''","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"The bill had easily passed the House and Senate with robust bipartisan support ;","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"however , conservatives in both houses railed against it ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"complaining","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"they had just seven hours","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"to read the 2,232-page bill , the `` length of two Bibles , ''","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Rep. Rod Blum","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"( R-IA )","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"wrote .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"The price tag ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"they say ,","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"is too high","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"and includes line items","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"they ca n't stomach ,","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"like money for Planned Parenthood .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Sen. Rand Paul had asked Trump to veto the bill ,","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"but in the end Trump decided to go ahead with the plan","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"as a possible government shutdown loomed .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"I agree","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"@ realDonaldTrump should veto this sad excuse for legislation","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"because it ' s $ 1.3 trillion in spending","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that ( almost ) no one read .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"https : //t.co/8aOSAOIESY -","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Senator Rand Paul","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"( @ RandPaul )","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"March 23 , 2018","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"An item in the measure","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that both sides celebrated","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"is the Taylor Force Act ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"named for an American combat veteran","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"brutally murdered by a Palestinian terrorist","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"while visiting Israel .","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"His killer was taken down by Israeli Defense Forces ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"but","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"when his body was returned to Ramallah","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"he was welcomed home a hero .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"`` The Palestinian government gave him a big sum of money .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"They rewarded him as a martyr .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"This bill , the Taylor Force Act , suspends all US money to the Palestinian Authority","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"until they change their laws","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"incentivizing their young people to kill Americans and Jews , ''","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"Sen. Graham told News .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"He calls it a `` sick system ''","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"that 's too lucrative for some Palestinians","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"to resist .","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"`` Under Palestinian law , you 'll make more money","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"being a terrorist than a worker , ''","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"When Taylor Force 's parents heard the news ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Graham says","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"they burst into tears .","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"They 've worked hard","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"to ensure","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"their son did n't die in vain .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"`` If you want your son to do all the right things ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"have them look up Taylor","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"because he did , ''","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"Taylor 's father , Stuart , told reporters","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"while lobbying for the bill .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Meanwhile , on the other end of Pennsylvania Avenue , there 's a shakeup in the president 's inner circle .","depth":5},{"id":85,"text":"He 's replacing his national security adviser , H.R . McMaster , with John Bolton , former US ambassador to the UN and outspoken hawk on foreign affairs .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"`` Well I think","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"that the national security adviser and the entire structure of national security decision-making in the United States is intended to be flexible ;","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"it is intended to be adaptable to the way","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"the incumbent president wants to structure it , ''","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Bolton said .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"McMaster will officially hand him the baton on April 9 .","depth":6},{"id":92,"text":"Bolton echoes Trump 's tough policies against North Korea ,","depth":6},{"id":93,"text":"coming in","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"as the administration plans a sensitive meeting between the president and North Korean dictator Kim Jong Un .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"His new position also increases the chance","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"the US will pull out of the Iran nuclear deal .","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Relations with China are also tense","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"after the president announced","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"he 'll charge tariffs on as much as $ 60 billion in Chinese imports to the US .","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"It 's a bold `` America First '' move .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"The president says","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"he 's trying to correct the nation 's $ 800 billion trade deficit with the world ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"half of which comes from China .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"`` When they charge 25 percent for a car to go in","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"and we charge 2 percent for their car to come into the United States ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"that 's not good .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"That 's how China rebuilt itself , ''","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"he said during his announcement on the tariffs .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"`` I really believe","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"they can not believe","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"they 've gotten away with this for so long , ''","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"he continued .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"China responded Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"announcing a list of American goods , like apples , pork and steel pipes ,","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"that they may hit with higher imports .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"It 's a move","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"they know","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"would hit the middle class ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"many of whom are Trump supporters ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"heading into the midterm elections and Trump 's re-election bid in 2020 .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"`` A trade war will not help anybody , ''","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"warned Cui Tiankai , Chinese ambassador to the US .","depth":9},{"id":123,"text":"`` It will certainly affect the daily lives of the American middle class people . ''","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"President Trump , however , says","depth":6},{"id":125,"text":"he 's doing things for the country","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"that should have been done long ago .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":253,"left":0,"right":252,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":209,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":142,"right":208,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":139,"right":141,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":132,"right":138,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":128,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":3,"right":130,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":129,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":138,"left":7,"right":137,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":8,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":133,"right":135,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":134,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":134,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nucleari